<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <style>
        /* Inline Styles for better email client compatibility */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4A90E2; /* A friendly blue */
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top-left-radius: 8px;
            border-top-right-radius: 8px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .content-box {
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content-box p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        .emoji-icon {
            font-size: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: block;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            color: #aaaaaa;
            padding: 15px;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>ðŸŽ‰ {{title}}</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content-box">
            <span class="emoji-icon">ðŸš€</span>
            <p>Hello,</p>
            <p style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: #1f78c2;">
                {{content}}
            </p>
            <p>
                Keep up the great work! Your users are loving what you're doing.
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top: 40px;">
                Sincerely,<br>
                The Spot Team
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            This is an automated notification. Please do not reply to this email.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>